2/ Requirement:

+ Delete all files in "folder_02"

+ Open file "ex_01.pl" by "VI" and compose a short script so as to copy "file_01" to "folder_02" and replace "PARAMETER_WIDTH" by 3

3/ How to run

   /usr/bin/perl ex_01.pl

4/ Expected result 

|--01_ex01
|     |
|     |--folder_01
|     |     |
|     |     |--file_01.v
|     |
|     |--folder_02
|           |
|           |--file_02.v  // In this file, the string "PARAMETER_WIDTH" is replaced by "3"
|     
|--ex_01.pl
